## Final State

- Root cause: `data-sync-job` (owned by `test-developer`, purpose ÔÇťdata synchronization testÔÇŁ) producing excessive log output and consuming ephemeral storage on `worker-node-03`.
- Job `data-sync-job` and its pod `data-sync-job-pod` have been deleted.
